    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - Omni Logistics India - Experienced Professionals",
    "description": "Omni Logistics India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Pune location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Omni Logistics India:\nOmni Logistics India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Omni Logistics India!",
